paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
table_list=[
	'ADDRTYPE',
	'AR',
	'ARDBCODE',
	'ARDBGRP',
	'ARDBT',
	'ARGRP',
	'ARINV',
	'ARPT',
	'CHANGWAT',
	'OCCPTN',
	'PTADDR',
	'PT',
	]
#dataframe dict
dd={}
for i in table_list:
	dd[i]=spark.read.csv(
    		path="data/poc/"+ i +".csv",
    		header=True,
    		inferSchema=True, 
    		timestampFormat="dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss",
    		mode="DROPMALFORMED",
	    )
	dd[i].registerTempTable(i)

df_province =spark.read.csv(
    		path="notebook/province.csv",
    		header=True,
    		inferSchema=True, 
    		timestampFormat="dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss",
    		mode="DROPMALFORMED",
	    )

paragraphs.title: เตรียมข้อมูล
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
from pyspark.sql.functions import year, mean, month

df = dd['AR'].select('arno','invno', 'invamt')\
    .withColumnRenamed("invamt", "ar_invamt")\
    .join(dd['ARINV'].select('invno','dbtno','invamt','rcptamt','argrp'), 'invno').distinct()\
    .withColumnRenamed("invamt", "arinv_invamt")\
    .withColumnRenamed("rcptamt", "arinv_rcptamt")\
    .join(dd['ARGRP'].select('argrp','name'), 'argrp')\
    .withColumnRenamed("name", "argrp_name")\
    #.join(dd['ARDBT'].select('dbtno','glcode','dvbtamt').distinct(), 'dbtno')\
    .join(dd['ARPT'].select('arno','hn','ardate'), 'arno')\
    
    .join(dd['PT'],'hn')\
    .join(dd['OCCPTN'].select('occptn','name'), 'occptn')\
    .withColumnRenamed("name", "occptn_name")\
    .join(dd['PTADDR'].select('hn','changwat'),'hn')\
    .join(dd['CHANGWAT'].select('changwat','name'),'changwat')\
    .drop('changwat')\
    .withColumnRenamed("name", "changwat_name")
    
basedf = df.join(df_province, df.changwat_name==df_province.CHANGWAT_T)
df=basedf
#print(df.count())

#print(df.dtypes)
z.show(df)

paragraphs.title: รวมยอดค่าใช้จ่าย (ปี-เดือน-ค่าใช้จ่าย)
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
from pyspark.sql.functions import year, mean, month
from pyspark.sql import functions as F
df2=dd['ARINV'].select('invno','dbtno','invamt','rcptamt','argrp','invdate').distinct()\
    .withColumnRenamed("invamt", "arinv_invamt")\
    .withColumnRenamed("rcptamt", "arinv_rcptamt")\
    .join(dd['ARGRP'].select('argrp','name'), 'argrp')\
    .withColumnRenamed("name", "argrp_name")\
    .groupby("argrp_name",year('invdate').alias("year"), month('invdate').alias("month"))\
    .agg(F.sum('arinv_invamt'),F.sum('arinv_rcptamt'))\
    .sort('sum(arinv_invamt)')

z.show(df2)
